title: Jenna Starborn
description: From the award-winning author of the Samaria trilogy-a classic story of a woman with the will to rise above the darkest secrets...  A baby harvested from the gen-tanks on the planet Baldus.  A girl scorned by the only family she has ever known.  A woman brave enough to follow her heart-wherever in the universe it may lead her.
author: Sharon Shinn
